{"tid":1687478,"cid":21,"subCid":8,"title":"點解台灣好多音樂機構都唔承認英國皇家ABRSM考試?","createTime":"2019-11-02T01:10:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T02:53:38.000Z","uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"687d302da07ece91703737b4414269792fac1c90","tid":1687478,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:10:54.000Z","msg":"ABRSM唔係世界公認ge咩?<br />\n本人諗住未來去台灣做下音樂演奏或者教育<br />\n但我去台灣PTT論壇查過下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/man/Musicteach/D48E/M.1085239988.A.23C.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fman%2FMusicteach%2FD48E%2FM.1085239988.A.23C.html&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8M83aCWJNbCOh4I0%2FkJBrkU%3D&h=9edbf3cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/man/Musicteach/D48E/M.1085239988.A.23C.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/piano/M.1418209557.A.9A3.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2Fpiano%2FM.1418209557.A.9A3.html&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8M83aCWJNbCOh4I0%2FkJBrkU%3D&h=3cf90c70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/piano/M.1418209557.A.9A3.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Musicteach/M.1252048511.A.3DC.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FMusicteach%2FM.1252048511.A.3DC.html&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8M83aCWJNbCOh4I0%2FkJBrkU%3D&h=cc5aee64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Musicteach/M.1252048511.A.3DC.html</a><br />\n先知原來台灣雖然都係有得考ABRSM，但就算考左，好多台灣音樂機構都唔會承認英國ABRSM所有術科考試<br />\n佢地只會承認佢地自己各間大學的音樂系或者日本YAMAHA公開音樂考試<br />\n<br />\n點解佢地只承認日本或者佢地本土而唔承認英國ABRSM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cecdc6d9779eb636c528c839b35c1b2fd92a7c39","tid":1687478,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T00:55:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4058d00852275114c2d4d4016390a87f627e9091","tid":1687478,"uid":336837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T02:53:38.000Z","msg":"好似話係因為主修音樂既台灣學生由細到大都係音樂班出身，覺得學校既音樂考試已經難過ABRSM，而且覺得ABRSM係啲比業餘同當音樂係興趣既人先考，所以台灣大學修音樂既大學面試都只係需要聽你演奏，唔似香港要考左8級先有得面試<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(之前係YouTube睇到個台灣主修鋼琴既人講"}]}